        <h2>Start Learning More Efficiently Today</h2>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Join thousands of smart learners who boosted their grades with AI assistance. Get started for free — no commitment.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" style="background: white; color:#3A0CA3;"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i> Join Free</a>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.7;">✓ Cancel anytime • Access to AI notes & more</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer with brand, quick links, contact, social icons -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="footer-content">
          <div class="footer-brand">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> StudyGenie</h3>
            <p>AI-powered learning for the modern student. Unlock your potential with adaptive study tools.</p>
